title: Nathan Gray from Boy Sets Fire

description:
Our favorite, Nathan Gray from Boy Sets Fire, returns for another interesting discussion about his life in and around music. Our last podcast was over six years ago, so we dove back in and discussed abuse, being engaged in art and starting small. Enjoy! Battle dehydration with DripDrop and get 20% if you use the code WORDS. The best way to share music is with the Earbuds Music app. It's free so download it today!
